# apps/web

- Session: `fetch(..., { credentials: 'include' })` — API sets httpOnly cookie
- Google sign-in per `docs/specs/authentication.md`
- No Playwright, no vault secrets in browser storage
- Task approval UI must show title, price, description before `POST /tasks/:id/approve`
